    "description": "Experience the ultimate in versatility with the Sit N’ Stand Double Stroller from Baby Trend. It comfortably seats two children, and the rear seat can be removed for use of the included jump seat or standing platform. The two ratcheting canopies provide excellent sun protection for both of your passengers. The parent tray features 2 cup holders and a covered storage compartment for small incidentals and the roomy storage basket holds larger items. Both full-sized seats are equipped with reclining seatbacks, child trays with cup holders, and 5-point safety harnesses. The padded jump seat also includes a 3-point safety harness. The 8\" EVA tires provide a smooth, comfortable ride and the lockable rear wheels provide stability on command. After your excursion, the Sit N’ Stand folds compact for convenient transport or storage.",
