    "description": "[3-In-1 Design For Growing Kids]This innovative 3-in-1 toddler push car features 3 modes (push car, remote control, and electric mode) that can be switched easily, catering to the riding needs of boys and girls aged 1-3.5 years. Parents can use the push mode to walk with kids in the park, while the remote control mode allows them to guide the car effortlessly. As kids grow, they can press the paddles on the 2 motors to switch to electric mode and ride anywhere. The adjustable push rod can be easily shortened when not in use [360° Spin & Colorful LED Light]Equipped with 3 universal wheels, this toddler push car with handle rotate 360° on the spot, letting kids to ride flexibly and freely even in tight indoor spaces. The front of the electric car for toddlers and the 2 large wear-resistant wheels are inlaid with colorful lights, and the dreamy lights make kids feel like they are wandering in the stars. (Note: Universal wheels are more suitable for driving on hard and flat roads.) [5-Point Safety Belt for Greater Safety]Compared with ordinary 2-point seat belts, the 5-point seat belt significantly improves both safety and comfort. The electric mode features 2 hidden lock switches on both sides of the motor, allowing parents to disable the function in advance and prevent accidental pedal activation by kids. Plus, the remote control includes an emergency stop function that lets parents immediately stop the baby car when needed to avoid potential hazards. The semi-enclosed body design reduces the risk of accidental falls, giving kids a greater sense of security",
    "Product_Description": "[3-In-1 Design For Growing Kids]This innovative 3-in-1 toddler push car features 3 modes (push car, remote control, and electric mode) that can be switched easily, catering to the riding needs of boys and girls aged 1-3.5 years. Parents can use the push mode to walk with kids in the park, while the remote control mode allows them to guide the car effortlessly. As kids grow, they can press the paddles on the 2 motors to switch to electric mode and ride anywhere. The adjustable push rod can be easily shortened when not in use [360° Spin & Colorful LED Light]Equipped with 3 universal wheels, this toddler push car with handle rotate 360° on the spot, letting kids to ride flexibly and freely even in tight indoor spaces. The front of the electric car for toddlers and the 2 large wear-resistant wheels are inlaid with colorful lights, and the dreamy lights make kids feel like they are wandering in the stars. (Note: Universal wheels are more suitable for driving on hard and flat roads.) [5-Point Safety Belt for Greater Safety]Compared with ordinary 2-point seat belts, the 5-point seat belt significantly improves both safety and comfort. The electric mode features 2 hidden lock switches on both sides of the motor, allowing parents to disable the function in advance and prevent accidental pedal activation by kids. Plus, the remote control includes an emergency stop function that lets parents immediately stop the baby car when needed to avoid potential hazards. The semi-enclosed body design reduces the risk of accidental falls, giving kids a greater sense of security",
