    "description": "【Official License & Immersive Retro Adventure】This kids' electric car perfectly recreates the classic styling and retro colors of the 1973 Ford F-150. Complete with bright LED headlights, realistic engine sounds, a functional steering wheel, and a music panel with Bluetooth & FM radio, it immerses young drivers in a realistic experience. Every detail is designed for immersive pretend play, they're not just driving, they're starring in their own outdoor adventure 【Powerful 24V 4WD for All Terrains】Move beyond the limitations of 12V or standard 24V 2WD car that struggle on grass and complex surfaces. Featuring a 24V 4WD system powered by four 100W motors, this ride on toy delivers superior torque and traction, smoothly carrying two children (total weight ≤130 lbs) uphill and over terrain like gravel, grass, or mud. An upgraded stable turning radius and a maximum speed limit of 4.3 mph ensure safe and controlled driving, preventing tipping on uneven ground 【Ends Sibling Fights, True 2-Seater Comfort】Unlike other cramped ride ons the market, this electric car for kids features newly upgraded, roomy 2 seats (20”L x 14”W x 7.1”H) that comfortably fit two children aged 3–8, turning\"my turn\" fights into cooperative adventures. More than just a play vehicle, it makes a perfect gift for birthdays, Children's Day, or Christmas, encouraging active play over screen time, building coordination, and sparking lasting joy",
