    "description": "The Dream On Me TableTalk 2-in-1 High Chair is thoughtfully designed to grow with your child, seamlessly transitioning from a baby feeding chair to a toddler chair with the included conversion kit. Created with both comfort and convenience in mind, it features dual removable feeding trays—a color-coordinated, dishwasher-safe top tray for easy cleanup and a secure base tray for added stability during mealtime. The chair folds flat for compact storage, with the tray neatly stored on the back, making it ideal for homes where space matters. A padded, easy-to-clean seat and a secure 5-point safety harness ensure your child stays comfortable and supported at every stage. Built to meet all ASTM and CPSC safety standards, the TableTalk High Chair measures 38\" H × 28\" W × 23\" D in high chair mode and 24\" H × 17.5\" W × 16\" D as a junior chair. Suitable for children from 6 months to 3 years and supporting up to 33 lbs, it also includes a 1-year manufacturer warranty for added peace of mind.",
