    "description": "Take both kids on any type of family outing with the BOB Gear Revolution(TM) Flex 3.0 Duallie Jogging Stroller. This travel stroller features a mountain bike-style suspension system and air-filled tires. The five-point harnesses on this compact double stroller have a no-rethread design to keep your child secure and allow easy height adjustments as your kids grow. The swivel-locking front wheel lets you maneuver this portable stroller easily through crowded streets and locks for stability when jogging, while the reflective accents keep you safe on all your journeys. Designed to transport two kids, this BOB double stroller has a 50-pound weight capacity per seat yet is slim enough to fit through standard doorways. The extra-large UPF 50+ canopies on this jogger stroller for toddlers and babies shield your little ones from the sun and include a magnetic “peek & chat” window. With a spacious cargo basket and 10 storage pockets, this BOB stroller offers plenty of room for all your gear.",
