    "description": "\"Turn any day into an adventure with the Jeep Classic Jogging Stroller. Perfect for daily errands or runs in the park, this versatile jogger can be used as standard jogging stroller or as a travel system with your infant car seat (car seat sold separately). Able to tackle the toughest terrain, this stroller effortlessly adjusts to varying surfaces with its suspension system with visible shock absorbers that will smooth out any bumps in the road (or trail!). Equipped with an adjustable UPF 50+ canopy, multi-position reclining seat, swing away child tray, two cup holders, reflective material for nighttime runs, and plenty of storage, the Jeep Classic Jogging Stroller is designed to keep parents and kids with an active lifestyle happy. And, when you need to take this jogging stroller with you on a day trip or vacation, it folds easily and has quick-release back wheels that allow for hassle-free storage. Recommended use: Infants up to 50 lbs. Since 1941, the Jeep Brand has been a symbol of freedom and expression. Influenced by a love of the great outdoors, Jeep kids’ products are created for little adventurers. Fits the following car seats (car seats sold separately): Graco SnugRide Click Connect 30, 35, 40 Evenflo Nurture Evenflo Embrace For Britax B-Safe 35 Car Seats, please use the J is for Jeep Brand Jogger Car Seat Adapter (sold separately)\"",
    "Product_Description": "\"Turn any day into an adventure with the Jeep Classic Jogging Stroller. Perfect for daily errands or runs in the park, this versatile jogger can be used as standard jogging stroller or as a travel system with your infant car seat (car seat sold separately). Able to tackle the toughest terrain, this stroller effortlessly adjusts to varying surfaces with its suspension system with visible shock absorbers that will smooth out any bumps in the road (or trail!). Equipped with an adjustable UPF 50+ canopy, multi-position reclining seat, swing away child tray, two cup holders, reflective material for nighttime runs, and plenty of storage, the Jeep Classic Jogging Stroller is designed to keep parents and kids with an active lifestyle happy. And, when you need to take this jogging stroller with you on a day trip or vacation, it folds easily and has quick-release back wheels that allow for hassle-free storage. Recommended use: Infants up to 50 lbs. Since 1941, the Jeep Brand has been a symbol of freedom and expression. Influenced by a love of the great outdoors, Jeep kids’ products are created for little adventurers. Fits the following car seats (car seats sold separately): Graco SnugRide Click Connect 30, 35, 40 Evenflo Nurture Evenflo Embrace For Britax B-Safe 35 Car Seats, please use the J is for Jeep Brand Jogger Car Seat Adapter (sold separately)\"",
