    "description": "Give your child the perfect first scooter experience with the Mini 3-Wheel Kids Scooter, designed for stability, safety, and endless fun. The lean-to-steer technology makes turning effortless and helps develop balance and coordination, while the three-wheel trike-style design ensures a steady and secure ride. With an adjustable T-bar handlebar offering four height settings, this scooter grows with your child making it long-lasting. Watch their excitement as the built-in LED light-up wheels glow in motion—no batteries required! The smooth-gliding engineered polyurethane wheels provide a quiet and stable ride, whether indoors or outdoors. The wide, anti-slip deck gives little feet plenty of room to stand securely, and the rear foot brake ensures easy and reliable stopping power for added safety. Designed for kids ages 2 and up, this scooter is built with durable and lightweight materials, making it easy to carry, store, and take on the go. Simple assembly means your little one will be scooting in no time! Whether it’s for daily adventures, playdates, or outdoor fun, the Mini 3-Wheel Kids Scooter is the perfect ride to keep them active, engaged, and smiling.",
