    "description": "The Radio Flyer Red Rider Trike is a cheerful, confidence-boosting first tricycle built for everyday adventures. Quiet-ride wheels keep trips smooth, while a sturdy steel frame and comfort-grip handlebars help little riders steer with control. As kids grow, the adjustable seat ensures a secure, comfy fit through the years. A covered rear storage bin invites imaginative play - pack favorite toys or collect treasures on the go - and the easy-carry seat handle makes transport simple for parents. Perfect for sidewalks, driveways, and outdoor rides, this toddler trike brings memory-making fun to toddlers ages 2.5-5. 49 lb maximum weight capacity. Radio Flyer is a Certified B Corp dedicated to durable products that inspire active play and warm family memories.",
