    "description": "Life with a little one is always on the move, and the Dream On Me Zodiak Portable Playard is designed to keep up with every moment. Created for modern, on-the-go families, this lightweight playard weighs just 16.6 lbs and folds easily into the included travel bag, making it simple to carry, store, or take along for vacations, visits to grandparents, or everyday adventures. Setting up the Zodiak Playard is quick and stress-free. With no tools required, it assembles in minutes and folds down just as easily for travel or storage. A strong, stable frame provides dependable support, giving parents confidence during daily routines at home or wherever the day takes them. Your child’s comfort and connection are always a priority. The playard features full breathable mesh sides that promote healthy airflow while allowing you to keep a clear view of your little one at all times. The open mesh design helps your child feel calm and connected to their surroundings, whether they’re resting or playing. Safety is thoughtfully built into every detail. Designed to meet ASTM safety standards, the Zodiak Playard creates a secure, comfortable environment for children under 35 inches in height and up to 30 lbs. Parents can rest easy knowing their child is supported in a well-ventilated, visible space. Inside, a spacious interior measuring 37” L x 27.5” W x 25.5” H provides plenty of room for play, rest, and diaper changes. The padded mattress offers a cozy, supportive surface, making the playard suitable for use from infant (6 months) through toddler stages. When life gets messy, cleanup is simple. The playard features a removable mattress cover and wipeable surfaces for quick and easy maintenance. It folds neatly into the included tote bag with compact folded dimensions of 7” W x 25.4” H, and is backed by a 1-year limited warranty for added peace of mind.",
