    "description": "Whether spending an afternoon running errands, navigating tight spaces or taking that long-awaited trip, transporting your little one is easier with the Chicco Liteway Lightweight Stroller. This toddler stroller boasts a backrest with four positions that conveniently adjusts with one hand, allowing your child to recline or sit up to view the action, while an adjustable leg rest adds calf support. An adjustable, removable canopy with peek-a-boo window creates shade from the sun. Additional features include padded handles, a removable parent cup holder, storage basket and zippered storage compartment. Rear-wheel suspension and swivel-capable front wheels help maintain a smooth ride from surface to surface, and toe-tap brakes keep the stroller in place when parked. The lightweight aluminum frame, compact fold, and carry handle allow you to pop this travel stroller in and out of the car, making every trip just a little simpler.",
