    "description": "The Dream On Me Volgo Twin Baby Stroller keeps outings with twins or siblings manageable for daily errands, family trips, or anything in between. At 29.9\" wide, this narrow double stroller fits through standard doorways and moves easily through stores and sidewalks. Reclining seats with adjustable footrests fit children 6 to 36 months, up to 40 lbs per seat. Soft Ride wheels, 360° swivel front wheels, and lockable rear wheels keep on-the-go parents in control. The stroller measures L 31.8\" x W 29.9\" x H 39.3\", 22.57 lbs weight when fully assembled, offering a compact footprint for everyday use. Adjustable mesh canopies and large storage pockets handle sun coverage and everyday carry. Padded 5-point harnesses and an ASTM-tested frame built for real family life.",
