    "description": "The Evenflo Pivot Modular Travel System is an exceptional multipurpose car seat and carriage combo system. It was developed to exceed safety standards with the valuable input of parents for everyday use, is made from high-quality materials, and has numerous child and parent-friendly features. This sleek and versatile travel stroller and car seat includes the SafeMax Infant Car Seat and Safe Zone Base. The SafeMax Infant Car Seat has been developed with an anti-rebound bar that limits the amount of rebound movement experienced during a frontal impact. This full-size travel stroller also includes a modular frame with 6 modes of use. It’s reversible, allowing baby to face in or out, while the seat can easily convert to carriage, travel system, and frame stroller modes.",
