    "description": "Bring your dream nursery to life with the Graco Benton 5-in-1 Convertible Crib. With its timeless design, the Benton is the perfect addition to any nursery. The Benton is crafted from pine wood, engineered wood, and wood composites, and its applied finish has been tested to meet or exceed the applicable ASTM and CPSIA safety standards. The Benton is GREENGUARD Gold Certified and JPMA Certified. The Benton includes an adjustable mattress support base with 4 height options [note, this crib may only be used until your child can easily climb out or is taller than 35 inches (89 cm)]. The Benton can be converted from a crib to a toddler bed [Graco Toddler Safety Guardrail Kit (Slats) (01340-60 Series) sold separately], daybed, and full-size bed with headboard and optional footboard (full-size bed conversion kit sold separately). The Benton fits any standard full-size crib & toddler mattress (mattress sold separately –Graco crib mattress recommended). Graco is the recipient of the PTPA Seal of Approval and 2021-2023 Women's Choice Award for 9 out of 10 Recommended Baby & Kids Furniture. Backed by a 1-year limited manufacturer’s warranty. Assembly required. Mattress, toddler safety guardrail kit, and full-size bed conversion kit each sold separately.",
