    "description": "GREENGUARD Gold Certified, comfortably soft, and durably designed for real life in the nursery – introducing the Graco Premium Waterproof Crib and Toddler Mattress Protector, available in both 1-pack and 2-pack offerings. Designed to fit any standard full-size crib and toddler mattress, the Graco Premium Waterproof Crib and Toddler Mattress Protector is GREENGUARD Gold Certified, has a PVC-free waterproof sleep surface, is comfortably soft, and is machine-washable and dryer-friendly. Unlike other crib mattress protectors, the Graco Premium Waterproof Crib and Toddler Mattress Protector is soft and comfortable, and its elasticized bottom makes for a snug fit on your crib or toddler mattress. For the perfect match, pair your Graco Premium Waterproof Crib and Toddler Mattress Protector with the Graco Premium Foam Crib & Toddler Mattress – America’s #1 crib mattress* (*Based on dollars sold, according to 2019-2023 market data compiled by Circana). The Graco Premium Waterproof Crib and Toddler Mattress Protector is backed by a 5-year limited manufacturer’s warranty, and a supportive Customer Care team. Materials: 100% polyester (with PVC-free TPU coating). Exclusively from Graco, proud recipient of the Parent Tested Parent Approved (PTPA) Seal of Approval.",
