    "description": "This best-selling Kolcraft light weight and compact stroller for travel is designed for families on the go and is only 13 lbs which makes it perfect for travel around your neighborhood, across town, or while on vacation with your child Parents love the multi-position reclining seat so baby stays comfortable during day trips or while traveling. Plus, a large, easy-access storage basket keeps all of babys necessities nearby, and the parent tray includes two drink holders and a separate roomy storage area for your items. The three-tier, extended canopy provides extra sun coverage and a peek-a-boo window let's you easily check on your child while on the go. All-terrain wheels and front suspension give your little toddler a smooth ride and the 5-point safety harness can be adjusted as your child grows. The small collapsible foldable stroller features a convenient child tray with drink holder is removable for easy access to the seat. One-Year Manufacturer Warranty included. Maximum child weight recommended for this umbrella stroller is 50 lbs. Disney Size Approved and a perfect stroller for airplane travel (Though we do recommend always checking with your airline first). The best stroller for toddlers 1-3 - Use only once the child is able to sit up unassisted & has full head and neck control. Toddler stroller NOT compatible with Infant Car Seats. Affordable without Compromising Quality - a Baby Registry Must Have. Voted Best Lightweight Stroller for Traveling!",
